Thunder_Kick.help: You strike your opponent with a fast kick that causes smashing damage. The speed of this attack could catch your opponent unawares, stunning them briefly.
Thunder_Kick.shortHelp: Melee, Moderate DMG (Smashing), Chance to Stun (Foe)

Storm_Kick.help: You strike your opponent with a roundhouse kick that causes smashing damage and has the chance to knock the target down.
Storm_Kick.shortHelp: Melee, High DMG (Smashing), Chance for Knockdown (Foe)

Dull_Pain.help: Channeling your personal training, you become nearly impervious to pain. This has the effect of increasing your maximum hitpoints for a time.

Aimed_Shot.help: You fire a well aimed shot at a single target, causing lethal damage.
Aimed_Shot.targetHelp: Though it takes longer to execute, your Aimed Shot deals greater damage than the Talon Snap Shot. Damage: High, Recharge: Moderate
